[page]
<div class="author">Interview and flavor by <a href="/forums/member.php?u=108993">Jellicent</a>. Art by <a href="/forums/member.php?u=73434">Bummer</a> and <a href="/forums/member.php?u=173369">Magistrum</a>.</div>
